# Cursor Rules for Wise0wl Launcher

## Project Overview
This is a Tauri application with React frontend using Material UI. The project uses:
- Tauri (Rust backend)
- React + TypeScript (frontend)
- Material UI (UI component library)
- Vite (build tool)

