## Key Guidelines

### Material UI Usage
- Use [Material UI](https://mui.com/material-ui/) as the primary UI library
- Install: `npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled`
- Follow Material Design principles
- Use MUI's theming system for consistent styling
- Implement responsive design with MUI breakpoints

### Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all frontend code
- Follow Rust conventions for backend code
- Use functional components with hooks
- Implement proper error handling
- Add meaningful comments for complex logic

### Security & Performance
- Follow Tauri security model
- Validate all user inputs
- Use proper authentication handling
- Optimize bundle size and performance
- Implement proper loading states

### User Experience
- Create intuitive, modern interfaces
- Ensure accessibility compliance
- Provide clear feedback and notifications
- Support both light and dark themes
- Implement responsive design

